simple map of cancer rates world wide

Source: R/cancer_map_world.R
cancer_map_world.Rd

simple map of cancer rates world wide

cancer_map_world(world_tab = world_cancer_2020_all)

Arguments

world_tab

a data.frame as produced by gco.iarc.fr

Note

used https://gco.iarc.fr/today/online-analysis-map table CSV exports, some cleanup of special characters

Examples

data(world_cancer_2020_all)
cancer_map_world()
#> Warning: Data contains 5 rows with either missing or invalid lat/lon values and will be ignored
